Display of your actions, messages, and chat contributions to other Users as part of providing the Game to You.
Use of aggregated Device Information and Game data for analytical purposes.
You acknowledge and agree that PerBlue may share Personal Information, Device Information, and information collected from the Websites with PerBlue’s agents, corporate affiliates, or advisors who help PerBlue operate and improve its business. PerBlue has entered into or will enter into written agreements with its agents, corporate affiliates, and advisors to which it discloses Personal Information, Device Information, and information collected from the Websites that requires them to adhere to pertinent provisions of this Privacy Policy. PerBlue also prohibits its agents, corporate affiliates, and advisors from using any information disclosed to them by PerBlue for purposes other than implementing PerBlue’s instructions.
We will share some of the information we collect from You with vendors and other service providers who work with us to support the internal operations of our website and/or mobile application. For example:
We use a third party service for ad tracking and to help us prepare website and mobile application analytics. Our third party ad tracking and analytics company never sends emails, notifications, or other communications to our end users. If you would like to opt out of third party ad tracking and analytics, for Android Users go here: https://support.google.com/ads/answer/2662922?hl=en for iOS Users go here: https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202074. Your choice to opt out of ad tracking and analytics services does not limit our ability to collect other information from you for other vendors, subject to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
