PerBlue may use or disclose Personal Information, Device Information, and information collected through e-mail or from the Websites: to comply with applicable laws; to protect the rights and property of PerBlue or others; to protect a person's safety; to prevent abuse; as evidence in legal proceedings; to cooperate with properly authorized law enforcement investigations; and in response to subpoenas from third parties. If permitted by law, PerBlue will use good faith efforts to promptly notify a User of any subpoena that seeks any of the User's Personal Information or Device Information to enable the User to seek to quash the subpoena.
