If PerBlue learns that Personal Information of persons less than 13-years-of-age has been collected through the Game, then PerBlue will take the appropriate steps to delete this information. If you are a parent or guardian and discover that your child under the age of 18 has obtained a Game account against your wishes or without your consent, then you may alert PerBlue at legal@perblue.com and request that PerBlue delete that child's Device Information, Personal Information, and account from its systems.
